MISTS OF THE MOONS

   By means of this spell, the caster causes pillars of
   mist, illuminated by moonlight, to rise out of the
   ground.  The shadows the moonlight casts make the
   images resemble the mage, increasing his chance to
   dodge enemy attacks!  The images will slowly vanish
   over time, reducing the bonus; when the last image
   is gone, the spell is ended.

 GL: 6  COST: 10+(GL*4)
